FBIS4-15895 "drsov071_n_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-071 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 Turkmenistan New Presidential Press Secretary Appointed New Presidential Press Secretary Appointed LD1304091194 LD1304091194 BFN [Editorial Report] Ashgabat Radio Ashgabat Network in Russian at 0200 GMT on 13 April 1994 broadcasts a two-minute report about an edict by President Niyazov that has relieved Durdymukhammet Gurbanov of his post as presidential press secretary and appointed him chief editor of the journal YASHLYK. Kakamyrat Ballyyev has been appointed the presidential press secretary of Turkmenistan. He will also fulfill the duties of deputy chairman of the Turkmenistan National Tele-Radio Company.
